- **GitHub Repository**: [liaoliaots/nestjs-redis](https://github.com/liaoliaots/nestjs-redis)
- **Latest Version**: Check the repository for the latest release.
- **Key Config Options**:
  - `host`: Redis host address.
  - `port`: Redis port number.
  - `sentinelOptions`: Sentinel configuration options.
  - `clusterOptions`: Cluster configuration options.
- **CLI Commands**:
  - Install: `npm install @liaoliaots/nestjs-redis`
  - Test: `npm test` (Ensure you have the necessary tests set up)
- **Example Usage**:
  ```typescript
  import { Module } from '@nestjs/common';
  import { RedisModule } from '@liaoliaots/nestjs-redis';

  @Module({
    imports: [
      RedisModule.forRoot({
        sentinels: [{ host: '127.0.0.1', port: 26379 }],
        name: 'mymaster',
      }),
    ],
  })
  export class AppModule {}
  ```
- **Documentation**: Explore the [official documentation](https://github.com/liaoliaots/nestjs-redis#readme) for detailed usage and examples.
